[2026-07-02T05:20:13.858Z] [INFO] [stdout] 
[2026-07-02T05:20:13.858Z] [INFO] [stdout] **Root cause**: `applyAccentColor()` always set `--color-primary` (and related vars) as inline styles on `<html>`. These inline styles have higher specificity than the `.dark` class in `theme.css`. Even with the default accent color (`#2563eb`), the inline style overrode the dark-mode-appropriate `--color-primary: #3b82f6`, making primary-colored UI elements too dark in dark mode.
